<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="az">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>500 - Server Xətası</title>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap/5.3.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a1a 0%, #2d0a0a 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        body::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.1) 0%, transparent 50%);
            animation: pulse 4s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        
        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% {
                opacity: 0.3;
            }
            50% {
                opacity: 0.6;
            }
        }
        
        .error-container {
            background: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.95);
            border: 2px solid #dc143c;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.4), 0 0 100px rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.2);
            padding: 50px;
            max-width: 600px;
            text-align: center;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
        
        .error-code {
            font-size: 120px;
            font-weight: 900;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc143c 0%, #8b0000 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
            margin: 0;
            line-height: 1;
            animation: glitch 3s ease-in-out infinite;
            text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.5);
        }
        
        @keyframes glitch {
            0%, 100% {
                transform: translate(0);
            }
            20% {
                transform: translate(-2px, 2px);
            }
            40% {
                transform: translate(-2px, -2px);
            }
            60% {
                transform: translate(2px, 2px);
            }
            80% {
                transform: translate(2px, -2px);
            }
        }
        
        .error-icon {
            font-size: 80px;
            color: #dc143c;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            animation: danger 2s ease-in-out infinite;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 20px rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.6));
        }
        
        @keyframes danger {
            0%, 100% {
                transform: scale(1);
                filter: drop-shadow(0 0 20px rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.6));
            }
            50% {
                transform: scale(1.1);
                filter: drop-shadow(0 0 30px rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.9));
            }
        }
        
        .error-title {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.5);
        }
        
        .error-description {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #cccccc;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .btn-custom {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc143c 0%, #8b0000 100%);
            border: none;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            font-size: 18px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.3);
        }
        
        .btn-custom:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.6), 0 0 30px rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.4);
            color: white;
        }
        
        .btn-outline-custom {
            background: transparent;
            border: 2px solid #dc143c;
            color: #dc143c;
            padding: 13px 38px;
            font-size: 18px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        
        .btn-outline-custom:hover {
            background: #dc143c;
            color: white;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.5);
        }
        
        .error-details {
            background: rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid #dc143c;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            text-align: left;
        }
        
        .error-details h3 {
            color: #dc143c;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        
        .error-details ul {
            color: #cccccc;
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        
        .error-details li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .loading-dots {
            display: inline-flex;
            gap: 5px;
            margin-left: 10px;
        }
        
        .loading-dots span {
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            background: #dc143c;
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: bounce 1.4s infinite ease-in-out both;
        }
        
        .loading-dots span:nth-child(1) {
            animation-delay: -0.32s;
        }
        
        .loading-dots span:nth-child(2) {
            animation-delay: -0.16s;
        }
        
        @keyframes bounce {
            0%, 80%, 100% {
                transform: scale(0);
            }
            40% {
                transform: scale(1);
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <i class="fas fa-server error-icon"></i>
        <h1 class="error-code">500</h1>
        <h2 class="error-title">Server Xətası</h2>
        <p class="error-description">
            Üzr istəyirik, serverimiz hazırda istəyinizi işləyə bilmir. Texniki komandamız problemi həll etməyə çalışır.
        </p>
        
        <div class="error-details">
            <h3>
                <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i>
                Nə edə bilərsiniz?
            </h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Səhifəni yeniləyin</li>
                <li>Bir neçə dəqiqə gözləyib yenidən cəhd edin</li>
                <li>Ana səhifəyə qayıdın</li>
                <li>Problem davam edərsə, dəstək komandası ilə əlaqə saxlayın</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div style="margin-top: 30px;">
            <a href="/" class="btn-custom">
                <i class="fas fa-home"></i> Ana Səhifə
            </a>
            <button onclick="location.reload()" class="btn-outline-custom">
                <i class="fas fa-redo"></i> Yenilə
            </button>
        </div>
        
        <div style="margin-top: 20px; color: #888; font-size: 14px;">
            <span>Problem həll edilir</span>
            <div class="loading-dots">
                <span></span>
                <span></span>
                <span></span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap/5.3.2/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>